    "body": "- [x] `spack config edit` and `spack config get` now edit/dump `spack.yaml` in an active environment\r\n- [x] some bugfixes for `spack find -c` when used in an environment\r\n- [x] `spack install` in an environment would add a concretized spec as a root; fix that\r\n- [x] `uninstall`, used in an environment, now removes instead of uninstalling if the spec is still needed by another environment or package.  If it's not needed, we uninstall.\r\n    - This is not garbage collection (yet) but close.\r\n- [x] more tests",
